"{\n  \"text\": \"Hey everybody, Scotty here. Today we went to Alvin, Texas to a horse farm, and it's oh so beautiful out there to pick up a bunch of horse manure which she had tons of. And she helped us out greatly by getting her tractor and scooping it all up uh for free because it's just piling up on her property. Look at the steam coming off that so fresh, so active. That's it already starting to compost and uh the thermophilic bacteria breaking it down, that's where the heat's coming from. She loaded up onto our trailer that we got just for this purpose. We strapped it down real tight so that it didn't go anywhere, even though it's pretty heavy, it doesn't really fly away. We drove it back to Neveville, Texas, where our regenerative agriculture project is, and we scooped it or uh pitched it onto our flat pile. Our flat pile is not as active as we want it to be because we put a bunch of uh whole cabbage heads on there and they're just not breaking down because they're not chopped up. It's about knee high or thigh high really, and uh we're soon going to be putting that onto our pipes right here. This is the old compost, and that's about to go into another pile where it will cure.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" Hey everybody, Scotty here.\",\n      \"start\": 0.24,\n      \"end\": 1.6,\n      \"duration\": 1.36,\n      \"confidence\": 0.988,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" He\",\n          \"start\": 0.24,\n          \"end\": 0.32,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 0.993\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"y\",\n          \"start\": 0.32,\n          \"end\": 0.4,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 0.999\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" ever\",\n          \"start\": 0.48,\n          \"end\": 0.56,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"yb\",\n          \"start\": 0.56,\n          \"end